{"tid":1669154,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[國際文宣戰] 我搵到最爆既核彈題材可以助攻美帝Senators","createTime":"2019-10-22T11:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T14:45:57.000Z","uid":134925,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e56e8fad5944f4fc961d2c78fdc66c40a634e7","tid":1669154,"uid":134925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"首先睇下呢單新聞from bloomberg<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-10-18/lawmakers-slam-apple-for-censorship-of-apps-at-china-s-behest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-10-18%2Flawmakers-slam-apple-for-censorship-of-apps-at-china-s-behest&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=885374ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-10-18/lawmakers-slam-apple-for-censorship-of-apps-at-china-s-behest</a><br />\n<br />\n篇野重點係講 <span style=\"color: red;\">U.S. lawmakers from both parties slammed Apple Inc. and Chief Executive Officer Tim Cook on Friday for &ldquo;censorship of apps&rdquo; at the &ldquo;behest of the Chinese government.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Senators Ted Cruz, Ron Wyden, Tom Cotton, Marco Rubio and Representatives Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, Mike Gallagher and Tom Malinowski expressed concern about the removal of an app that let Hong Kong protesters track police movement in the city.</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;Apple&rsquo;s decisions last week to accommodate the Chinese government by taking down HKmaps is deeply concerning,&rdquo; they wrote in a letter to Cook, urging Apple to &ldquo;reverse course, to demonstrate that Apple puts values above market access, and to stand with the brave men and women fighting for basic rights and dignity in Hong Kong.&rdquo; Apple didn&rsquo;t respond to a request for comment on Friday.</span><br />\n<br />\n依家係連Senators Ted Cruz, Ron Wyden, Tom Cotton, Marco Rubio 都開到聲屌7 奶共tim cook呀，我地唔係咁都唔助攻呀嘛？我地係咪可以幫手係twitter 文宣係咁煲大apple為左奶共而下架左個睇住popo行動既app呀？？apple咁樣都唔算攪9我地d示威者咩？ apple聽晒中共話，咁同黨企有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n但就咁係twitter講可能都冇咩noise，我地班和理非可以係apple store前面示威，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和平理性</span></span>表達我地既不滿，apple為左奶共而下架左個睇住popo行動既app，然後吸引d外媒黎報道，d banner 可以寫返同一樣既訴求 urging Apple to &ldquo;reverse course, to demonstrate that Apple puts values above market access, and to stand with the brave men and women fighting for basic rights and dignity in Hong Kong.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n到時如果上左外國頭版，單野傳返去美國人度，tim cook就大撚獲啦，一定嚇到賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢到時冇得唔表態，但佢表唔表態都死，如果佢唔開聲，其實係等同默認奶共跪低，美國人一定會好不滿，佢去到邊都會追擊佢，但如果話支持香港人爭取民主，咁大陸人知道左之後一道會好撚嬲，會好似nba單野咁，會激起好大既民憤，我已經想像到，到時d小粉紅個玻璃心會碎晒，發晒顛，可能即刻打爆電話個mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，中共連nba單野都攪唔店，要咁低調處理，apple呢個核彈既威力仲爆過nba唔知幾多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家可以思考下個威力有幾爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果認同既請全力幫手推 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5faabbc831bb72858a45e2b28bdffd9ae25fdf8d","tid":1669154,"uid":31572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"49d0723e59dbc189c6179abb39616e6bf3efad95","tid":1669154,"uid":60434,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"唔好有痴線佬爆apple store就得"},{"pid":"be005