ld,&rdquo; she said.<br />\n<br />\nIt is questionable whether  she understands CCP deep enough!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>Media Team..... there are lots of media challenges!! </ins></em></strong>"},{"pid":"550128584749848660be3012666ed43cbe040490","tid":1669154,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:10:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d79b00a62443c7b4156365d8936f3f4f3010e71","tid":1669154,"uid":134925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd69cb5b5ae86f05dd551cc2b3d3d05b8b3c9091","tid":1669154,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9eac77fd5fdb9465c039b35418263c4f6d9b7c0","tid":1669154,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"其實HKmap.live放唔到香港地區,可以放喺其他地區,只要申請嗰個地區就download到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:53:21.000Z","msg":"個方法係精，但香港人可唔可以唔好一比人打壓就搵位走？企硬光明正大屌返對家得唔得？明明屬於自己嘅自由點解要讓步先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:42:11.000Z","msg":"so fking true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係&ldquo;Apple&rsquo;s decisions last week to accommodate the Chinese government by taking down HKmaps is deeply concerning<br />\n<br />\n有咩野公司會accommodate the Chinese government？ 黨企囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d127725af79c00331eb65003405560c3959c6b43","tid":1669154,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5815b9ca69028b8fcef914f3118bc94347e885d","tid":1669154,"uid":134925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550128584749848660be3012666ed43cbe040490","tid":1669154,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"